doctype html
head
  title Periscope
  style(type="text/css") @font-face {font-family: 'Lato';font-style: normal;font-weight: 400;src: local('Lato Regular'), local('Lato-Regular'), url(https://fonts.gstatic.com/s/lato/v13/8qcEw_nrk_5HEcCpYdJu8BTbgVql8nDJpwnrE27mub0.woff2) format('woff2');unicode-range: U+0100-024F, U+1E00-1EFF, U+20A0-20AB, U+20AD-20CF, U+2C60-2C7F, U+A720-A7FF;} body {font-family: "Lato", "Lucida Grande", "Lucida Sans Unicode", Tahoma, Sans-Serif;}
body(style="background-color:#f2f2f2")
  p &nbsp;
  center
    table(border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" width="650" style="background-color:white; border-collapse:collapse;")
      tr
        th
          img(src="https://s3.eu-central-1.amazonaws.com/periscopefiles/appFiles/mail_header.png" alt="Periscope")
      tr
        td(align="center" style="color:white;background-color:#4EE898;padding-top:75px;padding-left:50px;padding-right:50px")
          img(src="https://s3.eu-central-1.amazonaws.com/periscopefiles/appFiles/mail_bigbulletfriend.png")
      tr
        td(align="center" style="color:white;background-color:#4EE898;padding-top:40px;padding-left:100px;padding-right:100px")
          h1(style="font-size:2em;color:white;") <b> Bonjour #{destinationName}, </b>
          h1(style="font-weight:400;color:white;") #{senderName} voudrait t'inviter à rejoindre sa photothèque !
      tr
        td(align="center" style="font-size:16px;font-weight:light;color:white;background-color:#4EE898;padding-left:150px;padding-right:150px")
          p(style="color:white;font-size:16px;") Inscris-toi gratuitement et rejoins maintenant la photothèque de #{senderName} :
      tr
        td(align="center" style="font-weight:light;color:white;background-color:#4EE898;padding-top:20px;padding-left:100px;padding-right:100px")
          a(href=destinationLink target="_blank" style="font-size:16px;font-weight:400;font-family:Lato, Arial, sans-serif;color:#4EE898;text-decoration:none;border-radius:3px;background-color:white;border-top:12px solid white;border-bottom:12px solid white;border-right:18px solid white;border-left:18px solid white;display:inline-block;") Je m'inscris
          p &nbsp;
          p(style="color:white;font-size:16px;") <b>Dépêche-toi, ce lien n'est valide que 24h !</b>
          p(style="color:white;font-size:16px;line-height:150%;") Nous te souhaitons beaucoup de plaisir parmi nous,<br/><i>l'équipe Periscope.</i>
          p &nbsp;

      tr(align="center" style="background-color:#2e2e2e;font-size:12px;color:white;")
        td
          p(style="color:white;") <b>® Periscope</b>, 2450 Park Blvd, Palo Alto, CA 94306
  p &nbsp;